msgid "You can also run the default interactive file in the workspace:"
msgstr "也可以直接运行 workspace 中默认的 ``interactive.yaml``："

#: ../../en/quickstart.rst:112
msgid "Type ``exit``, ``quit``, or ``q`` to leave the chat."
msgstr "输入 ``exit``、``quit`` 或 ``q`` 退出对话。"

