msgid "Create a Prompt-Only State"
msgstr "生成 Prompt-Only 状态"

#: ../../en/quickstart.rst:117
msgid "Prompt-only mode is useful for lightweight experiments and API sessions because it freezes a case into a single system prompt without running the full dynamic initialization pipeline."
msgstr "Prompt-only 模式会把案例冻结成一个 system prompt，适合快速实验和 API session："

