msgid "Run Batch Experiments"
msgstr "批量运行"

#: ../../en/quickstart.rst:131
msgid "Prepare a script file containing counselor messages, then run a batch:"
msgstr "准备一个包含咨询师消息的脚本文件，然后运行批处理："

